comment.author: 77788549@N05
comment._content: Private Nathan formerly served as a Regular with the East Surreys as No 7030.  He transferred to the Tyneside Scottish as No 64388.

comment.author: 64288588@N05
comment._content:
Joseph Nathan was born in Holborn and enlisted in London.
There is a Joseph Thomas Nathan whose birth is registered in Holborn in March 1893.
